{"tid":463503,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"古天樂紐西蘭拍《真．三國無雙》","createTime":"2017-11-09T14:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T15:46:56.000Z","uid":41453,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e236487e70b04c67d960d0fcfe3029d18ad64a8b","tid":463503,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"古天樂之前因為拍《真．三國無雙》嘅真人電影版，不慎被兵器打傷右眼，要即時返香港就醫，眼球縫咗8針，之後戴住黑超出席活動，認真敬業。<br />\n<br />\n當日古仔話拆線要等多十日，好番要等三、四星期，計番時間，只係剛好過咗兩個星期，應該未好番晒。之前有報道指，古仔將會接演三國戰神呂布，簡單講，即係大Boss要不停打打打，導演周顯揚啱啱喺facebook表揚佢呢份打不死嘅精神，開post話：「古仔眼睛雖然未完全康復，但他仍然堅持帶傷復工，繼續進行《真．三國無雙》紐西蘭的拍攝他這份尊業精神及人格魅力，令我感動、令我佩服。」周顯揚又話發生傷眼意外當日嘅片段仍然瀝瀝在目：「意外那天他眼睛不停流血，還堅持勸我不要停拍，勸我繼續把戲拍完！」呢份專業精神，係難得嘅。<br />\n更難得嘅係，古仔未好番，已經急不及待跟住大隊去咗紐西蘭，見佢着住成套呂布戲服開工，但仍然要戴住黑超保護對眼，尤其係喺雪地更易令眼睛受傷，真係搵命搏。另外，喺呢啲大合照相入面，仲見到劉關張三兄弟嘅造型，不過神粹就唔夠呂布咁似喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510221194_6ac4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510221194_6ac4.jpg&h=1be5de57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510221196_a80b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510221196_a80b.jpg&h=b7ab89cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d03d5518cf1c94bcf91c9f0462680f04eb84bba2","tid":463503,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"見到周顯揚杜緻朗=唔洗睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202e706db38e950b4813358a2b422aa9b9b3c3df","tid":463503,"uid":44674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"他對導演說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上"},{"pid":"6ad958f93e978cfe39ba8d6d9de1ea1b90e74421","tid":463503,"uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他對導演說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上</blockquote><br />\n我來縫！"},{"pid":"999d50c496f541d5431c6f699b0e77ea67e5a428","tid":463503,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"個關羽咩料，成個道友咁"},{"pid":"94c6cb4a5fddf2489712705e245602a0b07b3a8e","tid":463503,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他對導演說：「找來300多人不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將酒精直接倒在傷口上</blockquote><br />\n我來倒"},{"pid":"24fff39b69776de5fc2009bad9d7a8878e4b2a1d","tid":463503,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"燒山好野"},{"pid":"c0cd5b508c15a05ee6a50c20c2bf978a82389da4","tid":463503,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;沒有嘗試過的人生"},{"pid":"e611e60327da20bfea67dcc99fbfd32d749fa820","tid":463503,"uid":13700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"眼球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e91299f59de080ec7059e157df20c325e789cde","tid":463503,"uid":14238,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"轉做夏候惇未得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bba20c6bc33d1908bfd4456c14e859de7b831c","tid":463503,"uid":9699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉做夏候惇未得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c83093d7a616e4a4e773b6e7329fcea1d4f1874","tid":463503,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime